<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFFE56A5AFDDA91991C5BBCD3" box="[550,603,1984,2017]" country="Cameroon" name="North" pageId="30" pageNumber="788">Not</collectingRegion>
assessed as a distinct species on The IUCN Red List, but makes up most of what was formerly recognized as 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFE56A5AFC5391B11A4AB33B" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1915" box="[943,1098,2024,2057]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Tylonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="788" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="robustula">T. robustula</taxonomicName>
, which was listed as Least Concern.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
